html_attributions: 富記海鮮酒家 Fu Kee Seafood Restaurant
富記海鮮酒家 Fu Kee Seafood Restaurant

reviews.text: A very nice restaurant for lunch amongst the very large choice alongside the harbour. Nice service, very efficient and the entire staff does speak English. Food is delightful, fresh although not all local such as the abalones, but is prepared with taste and usually quite quick. View is not amazing in the area but the atmosphere is peaceful, absolutely free of noise; a good destination for a weekend. Price wise, it's very reasonable given the quality and the size of portions. Definitely 5 ☆.

A very nice and friendly restaurant. Staff were attentive, polite and very helpful. Food was tasty and fresh and prices weren't too expensive. When we went it wasn't during regular meal times so there weren't a lot of people. Tables by the water were an added plus! Highly recommend if you're in the area!
Very nice and fresh seafood, good value for money too
